  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink17-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaṉ parattaiyiṟ pirintavaḻi, ‘ivvāṟu oḻukutalum āṭavarkku
          iyalpaṉṟē; nī itaṟku neñcu aḻikiṉṟatu eṉṉai?’ eṉṟa tōḻikkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink17">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> putaṉmicai nuṭaṅkum vēḻa veṇpū</l>
          <l> vicumpāṭu kurukiṟ ṟōṉṟu mūraṉ</l>
          <l> putuvōr mēvala ṉākaliṉ</l>
          <l> vaṟitā kiṉṟeṉ maṭaṅkeḻu neñcē.</l>


        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> Because the man from the village </l>
          <l rend='indent2'> where the white flowers of the wild-cane that sway on bushes </l>
          <l rend='indent2'> appear like egrets dancing in the sky</l>
          <l> Desires new girls,</l>
          <l> My innocent heart has become empty.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
